For the next four years,

20:35.392 --> 20:37.926
<i>we were the happiest</i>
<i>we'd ever been.</i>

20:37.928 --> 20:40.062
<i>I'd feed him...</i>

20:40.064 --> 20:41.396
<i>bathe him...</i>

20:41.398 --> 20:44.066
<i>and, of course,</i>
<i>there was endless</i>

20:44.068 --> 20:46.134
<i>magical lovemaking.</i>

20:46.136 --> 20:50.739
<i>Then, a few days ago,</i>
